# Climate Change {#climate-change}
Since the 19th century the climate of the european alps is changing dramatical. Temperature increased around 2 °C celsius and is expected to increase further (Fig. Y). The speed and intensity of climate change outpaces global warming (Dumont et al. 2025). That has multiple effects:

